column8: A POSSIBLE TORNADO WAS REPORTED ON ARKANSAS HIGHWAY 65 NORTH OF DAMASCUS. HIGHWAY 65 WAS CLOSED DUE TO TREES IN THE ROAD. TREES WERE REPORTED DOWN AND A TREE WAS ON A H (LZK)
